window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>International bestselling author Jeffery Deaver explores the borderline between lies and loyalty in a story of a brotherhood on the brink.</b></p> <p>In the wake of a disastrous firefight with a Mexican cartel, two El Paso police officers find themselves in a military hospital facing a debriefing about what went wrong. As their accounts unfold, Tony, a by-the-book cop, begins to believe that hotheaded Matt might have divided loyalties. Could he have intentionally led the team into a trap that saw the death of a beloved senior officer? Or is the truth even more terrifying than Tony dares to imagine?</p>"; 
